<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #0B132B; color: #FFFFFF; line-height: 1.6; padding: 40px; margin: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; background: #1A2235; border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px; border: 1px solid #2e3a59; }
        h1 { color: #0A6BFF; margin-top: 0; }
        h2 { color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 0; }
        p { color: #cbd5e1; }
        a { color: #7dd3fc; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #0A6BFF; color: #FFFFFF !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; }
        .panel { margin-top: 24px; background: rgba(10, 107, 255, 0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(10, 107, 255, 0.22); padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to SentinelFlow</h1>
        <p>Hi {!Lead.FirstName},</p>
        <p>Thank you for reaching out about SentinelFlow for {!Lead.Company}. SentinelFlow helps Salesforce teams detect incidents, understand business impact, and automate recovery workflows.</p>

        <div class="panel">
            <h2>Plans</h2>
            <p><strong>Starter:</strong> Free trial for small teams, basic monitoring, and community support.</p>
            <p><strong>Professional:</strong> $29/month early access pricing with unlimited incidents, AI classification, self-healing automation, observability dashboard, and priority support.</p>
            <p><strong>Enterprise:</strong> Custom pricing for multi-tenant isolation, advanced controls, dedicated support, and enterprise rollout.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="panel">
            <h2>Payment, Contact, and Terms</h2>
            <p><strong>Payment methods:</strong> Professional plan payments are collected through secure Stripe-hosted card checkout. SentinelFlow never stores card numbers or security codes.</p>
            <p><strong>Terms and conditions:</strong> Review the latest terms before payment at <a href="https://sentinelflow.onrender.com/terms.html">https://sentinelflow.onrender.com/terms.html</a>.</p>
            <p><strong>Contact:</strong> For billing, product, or installation questions, contact <a href="mailto:support@tomcodex.com">support@tomcodex.com</a> or visit <a href="https://sentinelflow.onrender.com/contact.html">Contact</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <p>After a paid Professional subscription is confirmed, we will send the Salesforce package installation link and setup instructions to this email address.</p>

        <a href="https://sentinelflow.onrender.com/#pricing" class="btn">View Plans</a>

        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 TomCodeX Inc. All rights reserved.<br />
            Salesforce AgentExchange Partner
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
